T1  - Online Auctions and Multichannel Retailing
AU  - Kuruzovich, Jason
AU  - Etzion, Hila
Y1  - 2017/05/15
PY  - 2017
DA  - 2018/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2017.2732
